===Hardware specification=== *CPU: [[Rockchip]] RK3566 @1.8GHz :Quad-Core ARM (Cortex-A55) *GPU: ''Mali-G52 2EE'' (OpenGL ES3.2); NPU 0.8Tops @INT8 :VPU (with 4K VP9 and 4K 10-bit H265/H264 decoding) *Storage: TF card (max.128GB)/MMC card slot *Memory: 1GB (LPDDR4) SDRAM (LPDDR4/4x 1/2/4/8GB) *Network: 1x 1GbE port *USB: 1x USB 2.0 (Type-C) Host, :1x USB 2.0 (Type-C) (OTG/Power) ports *GPIO: 1x 40-pin headers *Power Source: 5V/3A, USB (Type-C)
